Use this insert with any standard size muffin pan to bake delightful multi-colored cupcakes for special occasions, holidays, theme parties and more. Just fill the insert with colored batter to create festive, fun and delicious cupcakes. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: So this is the Wilton to town cupcake insert two piece set from bed bath and beyond. Create fun unique cupcakes for any occasion using the simple teuton cupcake insert. Simply insert the plastic form into your cupcake tin using two different colored batters. Simply fill the center ring with the first batter. Then fill the outer ring with the main batter. Once completed. Simply lift the insert straight up then bake cupcakes according to the batter recipe. The insert is top rack dishwasher safe the Wilton two tone cupcake insert two piece set available online or at a bed bath and beyond near you.
